    <img src="/mbimagespng/earngreen.png"><span class="maintext">
<h1>Earn Green!</h1>

<p>&nbsp;</p>
<ol type=1>
  <li>
    <p>Take at least 10 of the saplings that you have  grown while achieving the Grow Green MB to an official BSP sanctioned tree  planting activity/saplings buyer near your location.
    </p>
    <p>&nbsp; </p>
  <li>
  <p>Sell your saplings to the authorized BSP sapling  buyer at the planting area and earn some pocket money for your efforts.</p>  
<li>
  <p>Bring and plant your saplings to the designated  planting site.</p>
<li>
  <p>Record the following: (a) date of the tree planting activity; (b) vanue of the planting site; (c) number of trees sold and planted by the scout; and (e) signature and name of activity officer attesting to this activity.
  </p>
  <p>&nbsp; </p>
<li>If you have successfully sold and planted 10 or  more of your saplings, have your MB card below, signed by the MB counselor at  the designated planting activity site.
  <p>&nbsp; </p>
</ol>
<p>Note: The price for the purchase your saplings will  be based on the tree species, size and condition of your sapling. Please surf <strong><a href="http://www.scouts.org.ph/">www.scouts.org.ph</a></strong> for more details and schedule of planting activities nationwide.</p>
</span><p>
  </div>
